<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lonely-adj">lonely <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ləʊnli/    美 /'loʊnli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>孤独的；寂寞的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>lonely life</strong> in the country
孤寂的乡下生活</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She felt very lonely because she couldn't meet her friends.
她因为见不到朋友而感到很孤独。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-remote">2.★ <strong>人迹稀少的；荒凉的 (remote)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a lonely place / road
荒凉的地方/偏僻的道路</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>loneliness /'ləʊnlinəs/ n   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I experienced years of loneliness as a child.
孩提时，我经历了多年的孤独</p><footer>2020浙江</footer></div></div>